{
  "texts": [
    "Then, we conducted an experiment using the ChatGPT interface to test the generative, creative and comprehensive potential of chatbots in creative writing.",
    "The main writing tasks were identified, such as creating ideas and concepts, developing the plot and characters, writing dialogue, making a description and creating an appropriate atmosphere, and adding stylistic devices.",
    "According to these functions, five coherent story concepts in different genres (children, young adult, romance, fantasy and detective) were developed using ChatGPT (Figure 1).",
    "Our research method is based on a gradual creative writing process, from the general idea to the stylistic devices' development within one chat.",
    "ChatGPT proposes an idea of the story from the first prompt in the view of generalization as fundamental for AI agents' operations."
  ]
}